<h2>Digital Mode Note</h2>

<div class="info-box">
If you monitor our repeaters in analog and notice static or garbled talk, it's probably due to someone using the repeater in digital mode. Set the tone mode to "tone sql" to filter out the digital noise while still seeing when the repeater is active.
</div>

